{"type": "article", "id": 25707, "title": "海绵积木", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-20T07:00:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702152500que6VOT73t9Pg4pr.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">似乎很久没有玩过积木了，这组用海绵或浮石做成的“积木”倒是可以让成人使用。它的配色并不丰富绚丽，而是用红、蓝、粉、黑、白、灰这 6 种更成熟的颜色，可以放在浴池边上做装饰而不害怕掉到水中，多样化的模块足以拼出有趣的建筑。设计者是由 3 位女性组成的团队，<a href=\"http://www.deintuitiefabriek.nl/WATERSCAPE\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152456ISzVJF0nHtoykEb6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152457eHG9EfcP6ShA21Fi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152458AbmgzPq4KxNdvF2G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152458K76rvxhAG8ZLPJSO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 310px; width: 375px; left: 478px; top: 1097px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152459s0YQ8uVXnThw6Ced.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.82666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}